page.title: 15My house.
page.content: I live in a Semi-detached house on St.Leonards Rd.East.On the outside it is black and white.The garage is seperate from the house.From the outside you can see the lounge and two bedrooms.My front garden is small and my back garden is quite big the garden has a wall around.My front door is at the side of my house.The house is made from brick.Inside there are these rooms kitchen,dining room, lounge,3 bedrooms,and a bathroom.The lounge has magnolia walls and ceiling is woodchip.The carpet is a flowery pattern.The dining room is the same as the lounge.The kitchen has a lino floor,and wallpaper is pretend tiles. Upstairs the bedrooms are white and magnolia.In the bedrooms the carpets are red,green and brown.The bathroom is tiled in white and green with green carpet.The flight of stairs bend round
